
1  Kirucak akirot naka EJAKAIT abunore mama ejai Yona ebe, 
2  “Konyou, kolot Ninebe, ore ŋol loepol, kolimok ŋes akirot nakecorakin jo.”


3  Konyou Yona, kolot Ninebe, kwape ajaar akirot naka EJAKAIT. Kerai Ninebe ere loepol noi noi, loka alosit naka apaarasia auni. 
4  

Kogeu Yona alomar ore alosit naka adiopepaaran. Kiworo, kotema atiar, “Esalito apaarasia akaisaoŋon, kosodi konyet Ninebe atiyanakinio!” 
5  

Kiyuut ituŋa luka Ninebe Edeke; kolimosi ailuŋ, konapitos ipukoi, ageun ka lukapolok kiton ludidik kakesi.


6  

Kodolokis akiro ekabaka loka Ninebe, konyou koicoloŋoke loka ajakanut, kolac ekegoe, konap epuko, kiboikin okurwon. 
7  

Abu kolimo kitejen Ninebe kere ebe, “Kokisil loka ekabaka ka ikapolokoke; Sirikiir ituŋanan karaida itiaŋ, esipan loka aituk, karaida loka amerekekin, idiobore: sirikenyama, karaida aimat akipi; 
8  

Konye kimukoros kipukoi, ituŋanan ka itiaŋ da, kiwoneoto noi Edeke: eebo, kibelokinos kesi ŋinituŋanan ainyein ekerot loerono, anyoun da kadedeŋ naejai kakaninikec. 
9  Iŋai bo ejeni arai mam Edeke ibelokin iituni da, aibelokin ainyein akenyunyura naededeŋ, tetere mam kitwaki?”


10  Koany Edeke aswamisiokec, kwape ebelokinotor ainyein ekecerot loerono; kiitu Edeke kinyek aronis naabala iswamakini kes; mam abu kiswama.

